            . I have a house at No. 1, <placeName id="t18180401-186-crimeloc1054">Turner-street, Whitechapel</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180401-186-crimeloc1054" type="placeName" value="Turner-street, Whitechapel"></interp>
